latestIgtvVideos.title: Dental Treatment 😁 Before and After look😉
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Finally I'm done with my braces treatment for my teeth 😁I removed my braces on 31.12.2020 before new year 😁I'm happy to share this picture after removing the braces in the clinic called "Royal Dental care"the picture with "Dr.Ramesh" 🙏I'm so thankful to him 🙏💗I completed my treatment atlast feeling so much happy 😁🙏Now  I am very confident on smiling 👍Really I struggled a lot for this treatment to get this beautiful smile ,lots of pains inside the mouth and wounds then after 1 session I took off my 4 teeths and suffered with teeth pains n all for getting this beautiful smile 😑 finally it took one and half years 😮ufff 👍Now I got a very perfect smile 😁so Thanks to "Royal Dental care" Guys u will get a best treatment and Doctor was friendly and kind towards patient's so do visit and see this clinic with reasonable price and  happily finish your treatment here 👍
Duration of the braces which I was wearing from( May 15th  2019 to Dec 31st 2020) And I chose to wear " Ceramic braces"
Location: "Royal Dental care" Ramanathapuram, coimbatore 👍
DR.Ramesh Dentist 
For more details  contact this insta page :@drrameshdentist
